// PRAGMA journal_size_limit — caps the persistent rollback-journal size
// after a transaction commits.
// Spec §18.4 — journal_size_limit.
//
// Values:
//   -1   no limit (default)
//    0   truncate to zero after every commit
//    N>0 keep up to N bytes
// =============================================================================

